L-3 Communications Holdings Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















l-3 communications holdings inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Aerospace & Defense
Sub-Industry: Aircraft & Parts
L-3 Communications Holdings, Inc. is a prime contractor in command, control, communications, intelligence, surveillance and reconnaissance (C3ISR) systems, aircraft modernization and maintenance, and government services. The Company is also a provider of electronic systems used on military and commercial platforms. L-3's customers include the DoD, DHS, DoS, DoJ, and other agencies.




